{"type":"article_comment","id":403548,"parentType":"article","parentId":19998,"uid":8235,"contents":"回乡证已经沦落到拿来刮烛迹了<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/y98QiL4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y98QiL4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/y98QiL4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n【六四 31 周年．屯門】市民用回鄉證刮清燭跡<br>\n<br>\n每年六四晚會過後，都會有市民自發留下，清理蠟淚的痕跡。今年六四晚會被禁，悼念的市民分散各區，遍地開花，但這個「好習慣」仍留傳。<br>\n<br>\n晚上十時許，屯門公園悼念過後，尚有十餘名市民逗留，有市民自發清理地上的蠟燭。期間市民互相幫忙，有人準備垃圾袋，亦有人以回鄉證作工具，刮走地上的燭淚殘跡。<br>\n<br>\n不斷更新報道：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B-31-%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E9%97%96%E7%B6%AD%E5%9C%92%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E9%BB%9E%E7%87%AD%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">链接</a><br>\n直播專頁：https://live.thestandnews.com<br>\n<br>\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3141720969246835/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3141720969246835/</a>","date":"2020-06-04","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}